<h2>People</h2>

<p>Explore the web of litigants, jurists, attorneys, and community members. Browse people by categories: plaintiffs, defendants, and attorneys. Each person's page includes a set of attributes describing their status, color, sex, age, occupations, birth and death dates, and residences as stated in the court documents. Each attribute is sourced to the document. Every  relationship for each individual in the legal documents is also recorded here. Legal, occupational, family, and social connections to other individuals in the court records are visually presented in dynamic graphs.</p>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    
    <h3>Browse by letter</h3>
    <div class="browse_alpha_menu">
      <%= make_alphabet_menu(@alphabet) %>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /column-->

  <div class="col-md-6">

    <h3>Role</h3>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">Attorney</div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <!-- Browse by Attorney -->
        <%= form_tag person_browse_path do %>
        <% select_tag :id, options_for_select(@attorney_facet), :prompt => "Select Attorney", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br/>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">Plaintiff</div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <!-- Browse by Plaintiff -->
        <%= form_tag person_browse_path do %>
        <% select_tag :id, options_for_select(@plaintiff_facet), :prompt => "Select Plaintiff", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br/>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">Defendant</div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <!-- Browse by Defendant -->
        <%= form_tag person_browse_path do %>
        <% select_tag :id, options_for_select(@defendant_facet), :prompt => "Select Defendant", :class => "custom-dropdown__select", :onchange => "this.form.submit();" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /column-->
</div><!-- /row-->